:named REQ1_COMPONENT0_CAN_ALWAYS_GO_FROM_SATISFIED_TO_NOTSATISFIED)) ;; "has taken granulocyte-macrophage colony-stimulating factor within 30 days of study entry or plans to take granulocyte-macrophage colony-stimulating factor during the study, except for prednisone for patients with Pneumocystis carinii pneumonia and granulocyte colony-stimulating factor."

