:named REQ1_COMPONENT1_CAN_ALWAYS_GO_FROM_SATISFIED_TO_NOTSATISFIED)) ;; "has taken any investigational drug within 30 days of study entry or plans to take any investigational drug during the study, except for prednisone for patients with Pneumocystis carinii pneumonia and granulocyte colony-stimulating factor."

